<para>
    修复
<literal>CREATE TABLE dest AS SELECT * FROM src</> 或者<literal>INSERT INTO dest SELECT * FROM src</>期间
  TOAST相关数据损坏(Tom Lane)
</para>

     <!--
<para>
      If a table has been modified by <command>ALTER TABLE ADD COLUMN</>,
