     </para>
-->
<para>
   修复<quote>MergeAppend子目录列不匹配MergeAppend</>规划器错误(Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Fix index matching for operators with both collatable and noncollatable
