     </para>
-->
<para>
   使得<function>DatumGetInetP()</>解压有1字节头的inet数据，
   并且添加一个新宏，
   <function>DatumGetInetPP()</>确实没有(Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>

     <!--
<para>
      This change affects no core code, but might prevent crashes in add-on
